ERBB2


Description

Receptor tyrosine-protein kinase erbB-2 (ERBB2). Protein tyrosine kinase that is part of several cell surface receptor complexes. In the nucleus it is involved in transcriptional regulation. Enhances protein synthesis and cell growth.
